                  </hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">re-examined.</hi> I was present when the officer took him—I said he was the young man—I had described him to the officer—he said he was innocent—I am quite sure he is the person I saw take it—I knew him before—I have seen him selling things in the streets—I have known him twelve months—I left the omnibus in charge of the time-keeper.</p>
